name: Stay Young Tee
description:
Our 'Stay Young Tee' means so much to us and has become the slogan we have associated ourselves with. It represents our philosophy for the past couple of years and for the foreseeable future. Despite not being able to stay young with age, it is important to Stay Young at heart. 

Each t-shirt is: 

-Comfort fit
-Falls free from the body
-1x1 rib collar with elastane for perfect stretchability and shape retention
-Tagless
-Tubular fabric
-Shoulder-to-shoulder tape for superior support and seam stability
-100% ring-spun cotton
-115 gsm

Small - 36 Inch Chest
Medium - 38 Inch Chest
Large - 40/42 Inch Chest

Enjoy.

name: Golden State Pop Punk Tee
description:
Inspired by the birth place of pop punk, our 'Golden State Pop Punk Tee' is the result of our love and admiration for California and the impact it has had on music today. Each tee includes the names of the top pop punk bands in California today, including Blink-182, Green Day and The Story So Far.

Each t-shirt is: 

-Comfort fit
-Falls free from the body
-1x1 rib collar with elastane for perfect stretchability and shape retention
-Tagless
-Tubular fabric
-Shoulder-to-shoulder tape for superior support and seam stability
-100% ring-spun cotton
-115 gsm

Small - 36 Inch Chest
Medium - 38 Inch Chest

Enjoy.
